      <title>中国人民银行启动股票回购和股权置换工具以援助市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-18/pboc-starts-share-buyback-equity-swap-programs-to-boost-markets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国央行启动专项再贷款支持计划，帮助上市公司和大股东回购股票，这增强了市场对中国政府支持措施的乐观情绪，并推动股市上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-18/pboc-starts-share-buyback-equity-swap-programs-to-boost-markets</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 18 Oct 2024 03:11:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>数据显示经济放缓后中国采取措施支持市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-18/china-s-further-slowdown-highlights-urgency-for-more-stimulus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[就在数据显示中国经济增速为六个季度以来最低之际，中国央行却出台措施支撑市场，表明政府有意继续实施刺激措施，遏制经济放缓。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-18/china-s-further-slowdown-highlights-urgency-for-more-stimulus</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 18 Oct 2024 02:00:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
