    <item>
      <title>超级充电信贷市场是印度实现 5 万亿美元目标的关键</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/supercharging-credit-market-is-key-to-india-s-5-trillion-goals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度已经是世界上增长最快的主要经济体，目前正在推动更大幅度的扩张，以成为一个发达国家，而这一目标的关键在于扩大资本渠道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/supercharging-credit-market-is-key-to-india-s-5-trillion-goals</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>预测中国股市将反弹的策略师认为股市还有更多上涨空间</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/strategist-who-called-china-stock-rally-sees-room-for-more-gains</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国银行的一位期权策略师过去曾准确预测过股市上涨，现在他表示，今年中国股市的涨势可能还有更大的上涨空间。许多人都在为此做准备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/strategist-who-called-china-stock-rally-sees-room-for-more-gains</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 18:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
